<text><body>
<lb n="0781a20" ed="T"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0781a21"/>
<lb n="0781a22" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 512</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="T" n="0781a23"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead>佛說淨飯王般涅槃經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0781a24" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0781a25"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0781004" type="orig">〔宋居…譯〕－【聖】</note><app n="0781004" cb:word-count="8"><lem wit="【大】">宋居士沮渠京聲譯</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app></byline>
<lb ed="T" n="0781a26"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0781a2601">如是我聞：</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0781a2605">一時，佛住王舍城耆闍崛山中，與
<lb n="0781a27" ed="T"/>大比丘眾俱。爾時，世尊光明韑韑，喻若日
<lb ed="T" n="0781a28"/>出照明世間。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0781a2806" rend="inline">時，舍夷國王名曰淨飯——治以
<lb n="0781a29" ed="T"/>正法，禮德<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0781005" resp="Taisho">仁義＝二儀【聖】</note><app n="0781005"><lem wit="【大】">仁義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">二儀</rdg></app>，常行慈心——時被重病——身中
<pb xml:id="T14.0512.0781b" n="0781b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0781b01" ed="T"/>四大，同時俱作——殘害其<note place="foot text" n="0781006" type="orig" resp="Taisho">體＝身【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note type="mod" n="0781006" resp="CBETA">體＝身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0781006"><lem wit="【大】">體</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">身</rdg></app>，支節欲解，喘息
<lb ed="T" n="0781b02"/>不定，如<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">駃<note type="cf1">K19n0796_p0910a09</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">駛</rdg></app>水流。輔相宣令國中明醫，皆悉
<lb ed="T" n="0781b03"/>集會，瞻王所疾，隨病授藥，種種療治，無能
<lb n="0781b04" ed="T"/>愈者，瑞應<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0781007" place="foot text">已＝以【聖】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0781007" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->已＝以【聖】＊</note><app n="0781007"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">以</rdg></app>至，將死不久。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0781b0411">時王煩<note n="0781008" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">躁＝燥【聖】</note><app n="0781008"><lem wit="【大】">躁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">燥</rdg></app>，轉
<lb n="0781b05" ed="T"/>側不<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0781009" resp="Taisho">停＝亭【聖】</note><app n="0781009"><lem wit="【大】">停</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">亭</rdg></app>，如少水魚。夫人、<note place="foot text" n="0781010" type="orig" resp="Taisho">婇＝採【聖】</note><app n="0781010"><lem wit="【大】">婇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">採</rdg></app>女見其如是，益
<lb ed="T" n="0781b06"/>更愁惱。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0781b0604">時白飯王、<note type="orig" n="0781011" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔斛飯王〕－【宮】</note><app n="0781011"><lem wit="【大】">斛飯王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>、大稱王等，及諸
<lb n="0781b07" ed="T"/>群臣同發聲言：「今王設崩，永失覆護，國將
<lb ed="T" n="0781b08"/>虛弱。」王身戰動，脣口乾燥，語聲數絕，<note resp="Taisho" n="0781012" type="orig" place="foot text">眩目＝玄置【聖】</note><app n="0781012"><lem wit="【大】">眩目</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">玄置</rdg></app>
<lb n="0781b09" ed="T"/>淚下。時諸王等皆以敬意，長跪叉手，同共
<lb n="0781b10" ed="T"/>白言：「大王素性，不好作惡，經彈指頃，積德
<lb ed="T" n="0781b11"/>無厭，護養人民，莫不得安，名聞十方。大王
<lb n="0781b12" ed="T"/>今日，何故愁惱？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0781b1207">時淨飯王語聲<note place="foot text" n="0781013" type="orig" resp="Taisho">輒＝趣【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0781013"><lem wit="【大】">輒</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">趣</rdg></app>出，告
<lb n="0781b13" ed="T"/>諸王曰：「<note type="orig" n="0781014" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">我命雖逝＝我令雖斷【宮】</note><app n="0781014"><lem wit="【大】">我命雖逝</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">我令雖斷</rdg></app>，不以為苦，但恨不見我
<lb n="0781b14" ed="T"/>子悉達，又恨不見次子難陀，<note n="0781015" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0781015">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781015"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>除貪婬世
<lb n="0781b15" ed="T"/>間諸欲；復恨不見<note resp="Taisho" n="0781016" type="orig" place="foot text">斛飯王＝縠飯王【宮】＊</note><app n="0781016"><lem wit="【大】">斛飯王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">縠飯王</rdg></app>子阿難陀者，持
<lb ed="T" n="0781b16"/>佛法藏，一言不失；又恨不見孫子羅<note resp="Taisho" n="0781017" type="orig" place="foot text">云＝雲【三】【宮】＊</note><note type="mod" n="0781017" resp="CBETA">云＝雲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0781017"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雲</rdg></app>，年
<lb n="0781b17" ed="T"/>雖幼稚，神足純備，戒行無缺。吾設得見是
<lb ed="T" n="0781b18"/>諸子等，我病雖篤，未離生死，不以為苦。」諸
<lb n="0781b19" ed="T"/>在王邊，聞如是語，莫不啼泣，淚下如雨。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0781b1916" rend="inline">時
<lb n="0781b20" ed="T"/>白飯王，<note place="foot text" n="0781018" type="orig" resp="Taisho">答＝白【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0781018" resp="CBETA">答＝白【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781018"><lem wit="【大】">答</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">白</rdg></app>淨飯王言：「我聞世尊在王舍城
<lb ed="T" n="0781b21"/>耆闍崛山中，去此<note place="foot text" n="0781019" type="orig" resp="Taisho">懸＝玄【聖】＊</note><app n="0781019"><lem wit="【大】">懸</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">玄</rdg></app>遠，五十由旬。王今轉
<lb n="0781b22" ed="T"/>羸，設遣使者，道路<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0781020" resp="Taisho">懸邈＝懸遠【三】【宮】，玄邈【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0781020">懸邈＝懸遠【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝玄邈【聖】</note><app n="0781020"><lem wit="【大】">懸邈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">懸遠</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">玄邈</rdg></app>，懼恐遲晚，無所加
<lb ed="T" n="0781b23"/>益。<note type="orig" n="0781021" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">唯＝惟【三】【宮】下同</note><note type="mod" n="0781021" resp="CBETA">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0781021"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>願大王莫大愁悒、<app corresp="#0781019" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">懸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">玄</rdg></app>念諸子。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0781b2314" rend="inline">時，淨飯
<lb ed="T" n="0781b24"/>王聞是語已，垂淚而言，答白飯王：「我子等
<lb ed="T" n="0781b25"/>輩，雖復遼遠，意望不斷。所以者何？我子成
<lb n="0781b26" ed="T"/>佛，以大慈悲，恒以神通——天眼徹視，天耳洞
<lb ed="T" n="0781b27"/>聽——救接眾生應可度者，如有百千萬億眾生
<lb n="0781b28" ed="T"/>為水所溺，以慈愍心為作船筏而度脫之，
<lb n="0781b29" ed="T"/>終不勞疲。譬如有人為賊所圍，或值怨敵，惶
<pb ed="T" xml:id="T14.0512.0781c" n="0781c"/>
<lb n="0781c01" ed="T"/>怖失計，不望自濟，唯求救護，依有勢者，欲
<lb ed="T" n="0781c02"/>從<note resp="Taisho" n="0781022" type="orig" place="foot text">恐＝怨【聖】</note><app n="0781022"><lem wit="【大】">恐</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">怨</rdg></app>難而得解脫；譬<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0781023" place="foot text">如＝若【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0781023">如＝若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781023"><lem wit="【大】">如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">若</rdg></app>有人時得重病，欲
<lb ed="T" n="0781c03"/>得良醫以療其疾；如我今日望見世尊，亦
<lb n="0781c04" ed="T"/>復如是。所以然者？世尊晝夜，常以三時，恒
<lb ed="T" n="0781c05"/>以天眼，觀於眾生應受化者，以慈<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0781024" resp="Taisho">愍＝悲【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0781024">愍＝悲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781024"><lem wit="【大】">愍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悲</rdg></app>心，如
<lb ed="T" n="0781c06"/>母念子。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0781c0604" rend="inline">爾時，世尊在靈鷲山，天耳遙聞迦
<lb ed="T" n="0781c07"/><note n="0781025" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">維＝惟【聖】</note><app n="0781025"><lem wit="【大】">維</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">惟</rdg></app>羅<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0781026" resp="Taisho">衛＝越【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0781026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">衛＝越【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0781026"><lem wit="【大】">衛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">越</rdg></app>大城之中父王悒遲及諸王言，即
<lb n="0781c08" ed="T"/>以天眼遙見父王病臥著床，羸困憔悴，命欲
<lb ed="T" n="0781c09"/>向終，知父渴仰欲見諸子。</p>
<lb n="0781c10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0781c1001">爾時，世尊告難陀曰：「父王淨飯勝世間王，是
<lb ed="T" n="0781c11"/>我曹父。今得重病，宜當往見，餘命少在，時
<lb n="0781c12" ed="T"/>嚴<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0781027" type="orig">速＝欲【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note type="mod" n="0781027" resp="CBETA">速＝欲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0781027"><lem wit="【大】">速</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">欲</rdg></app>發。我曹應往，<note n="0781028" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">及＝曼【三】</note><note n="0781028" type="mod" resp="CBETA">及＝曼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781028"><lem wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">曼</rdg></app>命存在，<note n="0781029" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">得與＝及共【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0781029" resp="CBETA">得與＝及共【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781029"><lem wit="【大】">得與</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">及共</rdg></app>相見，
<lb n="0781c13" ed="T"/>令王願滿。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0781c1305" rend="inline">難陀受教，長跪作禮：「唯然，世尊！
<lb n="0781c14" ed="T"/>淨飯王者，是我曹父，所作奇特，能生聖子，
<lb ed="T" n="0781c15"/>利益世間，今宜往詣，報育養恩。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0781c1513">阿難合掌
<lb ed="T" n="0781c16"/>前白佛言：「我隨世尊<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0781030" place="foot text">貪＝會【三】</note><note type="mod" n="0781030" resp="CBETA">貪＝會【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781030"><lem wit="【大】">貪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">會</rdg></app>共相見。淨飯王者
<lb n="0781c17" ed="T"/>是我伯父，聽我出家為佛弟子，得佛為師，是
<lb ed="T" n="0781c18"/>故欲往。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0781c1804" rend="inline">羅<app corresp="#0781017" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">雲</rdg></app>復前而白佛言：「世尊雖是我
<lb n="0781c19" ed="T"/>父，棄國求道，我蒙祖王育養成就而得出
<lb ed="T" n="0781c20"/>家，是故欲往奉覲祖王。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0781c2010">佛言：「善哉，善哉！宜
<lb n="0781c21" ed="T"/>知是時，令王願滿。」</p>
<lb n="0781c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0781c2201">於<note resp="Taisho" n="0781031" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝時【三】【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0781031"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->是＝時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0781031"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">時</rdg></app>，世尊即以神足，猶如<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0781032">鴈＝鷹【宮】</note><app n="0781032"><lem wit="【大】">鴈</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">鷹</rdg></app>王<note resp="Taisho" n="0781033" type="orig" place="foot text">踊＝躍【聖】</note><app n="0781033"><lem wit="【大】">踊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">躍</rdg></app>身虛
<lb n="0781c23" ed="T"/>空，忽然而現在<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0781034" resp="Taisho">迦維＝迦惟【宋】【元】【宮】，加惟【聖】</note><note type="mod" n="0781034" resp="CBETA">迦維＝迦惟【宋】【元】【宮】，＝加惟【聖】</note><app n="0781034"><lem wit="【大】">迦維</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">迦惟</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">加惟</rdg></app>羅衛，放大光明。國中
<lb n="0781c24" ed="T"/>人民遙見佛來，皆共舉聲，涕淚而言：「設大
<lb ed="T" n="0781c25"/>王崩，舍夷國名必<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0781035" place="foot text">絕＝斷【三】【宮】，逝【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0781035">絕＝斷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝逝【聖】</note><app n="0781035"><lem wit="【大】">絕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">斷</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">逝</rdg></app>滅矣。」城中人民向佛
<lb n="0781c26" ed="T"/>啼哭，白世尊<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0781036" type="orig">〔言〕－【聖】</note><app n="0781036"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>：「爾時，太子踰出宮城，詣藍
<lb n="0781c27" ed="T"/>毘樹下而坐思惟，父王見之，稽首敬禮。大
<lb n="0781c28" ed="T"/>王如是命斷不久，唯願如來宜可時往及
<lb n="0781c29" ed="T"/>共相見。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0781c2904" rend="inline">國中人民宛轉自撲，哽咽啼哭，中
<pb xml:id="T14.0512.0782a" n="0782a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0782a01" ed="T"/>有自絕瓔珞<note resp="Taisho" n="0782001" type="orig" place="foot text">（之）＋者【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0782001" type="mod" resp="CBETA">（之）＋者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0782001"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">之者</rdg></app>，中有自裂壞衣服<app corresp="#0782001" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">之者</rdg></app>，中有
<lb n="0782a02" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" n="0782002" type="orig" place="foot text">（自㨑…者）十五字＝取灰土而自坌者中有自㨑拔其髮者【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782002" resp="CBETA">（自㨑…者）十五字＝取灰土而自坌者中有自㨑拔其髮者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app cb:word-count="15" n="0782002"><lem wit="【大】">自<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0782003" place="foot text">㨑＝縱【聖】</note><app n="0782003"><lem wit="【大】">㨑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">縱</rdg></app>拔其髮者，中有取灰土而自坌者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">取灰土而自坌者中有自㨑拔其髮者</rdg></app>，痛
<lb ed="T" n="0782a03"/>徹骨髓，猶<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">癲<note type="cf1">K19n0796_p0911a09</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">顛</rdg></app>狂人。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0782a0308" rend="inline">佛見是已，諫國中人：「無
<lb ed="T" n="0782a04"/>常<note place="foot text" n="0782004" type="orig" resp="Taisho">別離＝離別【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782004" resp="CBETA">別離＝離別【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782004"><lem wit="【大】">別離</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">離別</rdg></app>，古今有是。汝等諸人！當思念之，生
<lb ed="T" n="0782a05"/>死為苦，唯道是真。」佛以法雨灌眾<note n="0782005" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">生＝惱【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0782005" type="mod">生＝惱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782005"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惱</rdg></app>心，
<lb ed="T" n="0782a06"/>以種種法而開解之。</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0782a07"/><p xml:id="pT14p0782a0701">於是世尊即以十力、四無所畏、十八不共諸
<lb ed="T" n="0782a08"/>佛之法，放大光明；更復重以三十二相、八十
<lb ed="T" n="0782a09"/>種好，放大光明；<anchor xml:id="fxT14p0782a02"/>以從無量阿僧祇劫所作
<lb ed="T" n="0782a10"/>功德，放大光明。其光照曜，內外通達，周遍
<lb n="0782a11" ed="T"/>國界。光照王身，患苦得安，王遂怪言：「是何
<lb n="0782a12" ed="T"/>光<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782006">耶＝也【聖】</note><app n="0782006"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app>？為<note resp="Taisho" n="0782007" type="orig" place="foot text">日月光＝是日月光明耶【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782007" resp="CBETA">日月光＝是日月光明耶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782007"><lem wit="【大】">日月光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">是日月光明耶</rdg></app>、諸天光乎？光觸我身，如
<lb n="0782a13" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0782008" place="foot text">天＝入【宮】</note><app n="0782008"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">入</rdg></app>栴檀，令我身中患苦得息。我遂疑怪，<note place="foot text" n="0782009" type="orig" resp="Taisho">儻＝脫【聖】</note><app n="0782009"><lem wit="【大】">儻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">脫</rdg></app>
<lb n="0782a14" ed="T"/>是我子悉達來<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782010" type="orig">也＝耶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782010" type="mod" resp="CBETA">也＝耶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782010"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>，先現光明，是其瑞<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782011" type="orig">耳＝也【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0782011" type="mod">耳＝也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0782011"><lem wit="【大】">耳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">也</rdg></app>！」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0782a15"/><p xml:id="pT14p0782a1501">時，大稱王從外入宮，白大王言：「世尊<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0782012" place="foot text">已來＝來也【三】【宮】，以來【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782012">已來＝來也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝以來【聖】</note><app n="0782012"><lem wit="【大】">已來</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">來也</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">以來</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0782a16" ed="T"/>將諸弟子阿難、難陀、羅<app corresp="#0781017" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雲</rdg></app>之等，乘<note n="0782013" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">空＝虛【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782013" resp="CBETA">空＝虛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782013"><lem wit="【大】">空</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">虛</rdg></app>來至，
<lb n="0782a17" ed="T"/>王宜歡喜，捨愁毒心。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0782a1709">王聞佛來，敬意踊躍，
<lb n="0782a18" ed="T"/>不覺起坐。須臾之頃，佛便入宮。王見佛到，
<lb n="0782a19" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782014">遙＝豫【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782014">遙＝豫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782014"><lem wit="【大】">遙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">豫</rdg></app>舉兩手，接足而言：「唯願如來手觸我身，
<lb n="0782a20" ed="T"/>令我得安。為病所困，如<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782015">壓＝押【聖】</note><app n="0782015"><lem wit="【大】">壓</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">押</rdg></app>麻油，痛不可忍，
<lb ed="T" n="0782a21"/>我命將<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782016" resp="Taisho">逝＝斷【宮】</note><app n="0782016"><lem wit="【大】">逝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">斷</rdg></app>，寧可還反？我今最後得見世尊，
<lb n="0782a22" ed="T"/>痛<note resp="Taisho" n="0782017" type="orig" place="foot text">恨＝既【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782017">恨＝既【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782017"><lem wit="【大】">恨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">既</rdg></app>即除。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0782a2205" rend="inline">佛知父王病重羸瘦，色變難識，
<lb n="0782a23" ed="T"/>覩見<note place="foot text" n="0782018" type="orig" resp="Taisho">形＝刑【聖】</note><app n="0782018"><lem wit="【大】">形</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">刑</rdg></app>體憔悴叵<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782019" type="orig">看＋（佛）【聖】</note><app n="0782019"><lem wit="【大】">看</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">看佛</rdg></app>。佛告難陀：「觀王本
<lb n="0782a24" ed="T"/>時形體巍巍，<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782020" resp="Taisho">顏＝妙【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782020" type="mod" resp="CBETA">顏＝妙【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782020"><lem wit="【大】">顏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">妙</rdg></app>色端正，名聲遠聞，今得重
<lb ed="T" n="0782a25"/>病，乃不可識；端正形容、勇健之名，今何所
<lb n="0782a26" ed="T"/>在？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0782a2602" rend="inline">爾時，淨飯王一心合掌，歎世尊言：</p>
<lb n="0782a27" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT14p0782a2701" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「汝願已成就，</l><l>亦滿眾生願，</l>
<lb n="0782a28" ed="T"/><l>我今得重病，</l><l>願佛度我厄。</l>
<lb ed="T" n="0782a29"/><l>嚴飾瞿曇種，</l><l>汝為甚奇特，</l>
<pb ed="T" n="0782b" xml:id="T14.0512.0782b"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0782b01"/><l>末世說正法，</l><l>無護而作護。</l>
<lb n="0782b02" ed="T"/><l>法王以法味，</l><l>灌<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782021" resp="Taisho">澤＝濯【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0782021" type="mod">澤＝濯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782021"><lem wit="【大】">澤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">濯</rdg></app>諸眾生，</l>
<lb n="0782b03" ed="T"/><l>如是後<note n="0782022" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">世人＝聖王【三】【宮】，聖人【聖】</note><note type="mod" n="0782022" resp="CBETA">世人＝聖王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝聖人【聖】</note><app n="0782022"><lem wit="【大】">世人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">聖王</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">聖人</rdg></app>，</l><l>我子極慈孝。</l>
<lb n="0782b04" ed="T"/><l>人中之上寶，</l><l>名達大千界，</l>
<lb n="0782b05" ed="T"/><l>上至淨居天，</l><l>獨步無等雙。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0782b06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0782b0601">佛言：「唯願父王莫復愁<note resp="Taisho" n="0782023" type="orig" place="foot text">悒＝憂【三】【宮】，邑【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782023">悒＝憂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝邑【聖】</note><app n="0782023"><lem wit="【大】">悒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">憂</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">邑</rdg></app>！所以然者？道德
<lb n="0782b07" ed="T"/>純備，無有缺減。」佛從袈裟裏出金色臂，掌
<lb n="0782b08" ed="T"/>如蓮華，即以手著父王額上：「王是清淨、戒
<lb ed="T" n="0782b09"/>行之人，心垢<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782024">已＝以【宮】</note><app n="0782024"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>離，今應歡悅，不宜煩惱；當
<lb n="0782b10" ed="T"/>諦思念諸經法義，於不牢固得堅固志，<note place="foot text" n="0782025" type="orig" resp="Taisho">已＝以【三】【聖】＊【宮】</note><note n="0782025" type="mod" resp="CBETA">已＝以【宋】【元】【明】【聖】＊【宮】</note><app n="0782025"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】【宮】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>
<lb n="0782b11" ed="T"/>種善根。是故，大王！宜當<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782026" resp="Taisho">歡＝觀【聖】</note><app n="0782026"><lem wit="【大】">歡</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">觀</rdg></app>喜，命雖欲終，自
<lb ed="T" n="0782b12"/>可寬意。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0782b1204">時，大稱王以恭敬<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782027" type="orig">心＝意【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0782027" type="mod">心＝意【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782027"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">意</rdg></app>白淨飯王言：
<lb ed="T" n="0782b13"/>「佛是王子，神力具足，無與等者；次子難陀，
<lb n="0782b14" ed="T"/>亦是王子，已度生死諸欲之海，四道無礙；
<lb ed="T" n="0782b15"/><app type="star" corresp="#0781016"><lem wit="【大】">斛飯王</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">縠飯王</rdg></app>子阿難陀者，<app type="star" corresp="#0782025"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>服法味，佛所說
<lb n="0782b16" ed="T"/>法猶<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0782028" place="foot text">若＝如【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0782028" type="mod">若＝如【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782028"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>淵海，一句不忘，悉總持之；王孫羅
<lb ed="T" n="0782b17"/><app corresp="#0781017" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">雲</rdg></app>，道德純備，逮諸禪定，成四道果：是四
<lb ed="T" n="0782b18"/>子等，<app type="star" corresp="#0782025"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">以</rdg></app>壞魔網。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0782b1807" rend="inline">時，淨飯王聞是語已，歡喜
<lb ed="T" n="0782b19"/>踊躍，不能自勝，即以自手捉於佛手，著其
<lb ed="T" n="0782b20"/>心上。王於臥處<note type="orig" n="0782029" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔仰向…處〕八十字－【聖】</note><note n="0782029a" type="mod" resp="CBETA">〔仰向…捐棄〕七十六字－【聖】</note><app cb:word-count="76" n="0782029a"><lem wit="【大】">仰向合掌，白世尊言：「我瞻
<lb n="0782b21" ed="T"/>如來目<note resp="Taisho" n="0782030" type="orig" place="foot text">𥇒不眴＝睫不瞬【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782030" resp="CBETA">𥇒不眴＝睫不瞬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782030"><lem wit="【大】">𥇒不眴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">睫不瞬</rdg></app>，視之無厭，我願已滿，心意
<lb ed="T" n="0782b22"/>踊躍，從是<note place="foot text" n="0782031" type="orig" resp="Taisho">取＝臥【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0782031" type="mod">取＝臥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782031"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">臥</rdg></app>別。如來、至真多所<note place="foot text" n="0782032" type="orig" resp="Taisho">饒＝利【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782032" type="mod" resp="CBETA">饒＝利【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782032"><lem wit="【大】">饒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">利</rdg></app>益，其
<lb n="0782b23" ed="T"/>有得見、聞所說者，此輩之等皆是有相、大
<lb ed="T" n="0782b24"/>功德人。今日世尊是我之子，接遇過多，不
<lb ed="T" n="0782b25"/>見捐棄。」</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app></p><p xml:id="pT14p0782b2504" rend="inline"><note n="0782029b" type="mod" resp="CBETA">〔王於臥處〕四字－【聖】</note><app cb:word-count="4" n="0782029b"><lem wit="【大】">王於臥處</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>合掌心，禮世尊足下，時
<lb ed="T" n="0782b26"/>佛手掌故在王<note resp="Taisho" n="0782033" type="orig" place="foot text">心＋（上）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782033" resp="CBETA">心＋（上）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782033"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">心上</rdg></app>，無常對至，命盡氣絕，忽
<lb n="0782b27" ed="T"/>就後世。於是諸釋<note type="orig" n="0782034" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">䁺＝號【明】</note><note n="0782034" type="mod" resp="CBETA">䁺＝號【明】，＝㘁【麗-CB】【CB】</note><app n="0782034"><lem resp="CBETA.maha CBETA.say" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">㘁<note type="cf1">K19n0796_p0911c21</note><note type="cf2">T28n1546_p0025b29</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">䁺</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">號</rdg></app>咷啼哭，舉身自撲，兩
<lb ed="T" n="0782b28"/>手拍地，解<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782035">髻＝結【聖】</note><app n="0782035"><lem wit="【大】">髻</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">結</rdg></app>亂髮，同發聲言：「永失覆蓋。」<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0782036" place="foot text">〔中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782036" type="mod" resp="CBETA">〔中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782036"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0782b29"/>有自絕<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0782037" place="foot text">瓔＝纓【聖】</note><app n="0782037"><lem wit="【大】">瓔</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">纓</rdg></app>珞<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0782038" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782038">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782038"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>，中有<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0782039" place="foot text">〔自〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782039" resp="CBETA">〔自〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782039"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>裂壞衣<note type="orig" n="0782040" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">服＋（之）【三】，服＝嚴之【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782040">服＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】，服＝嚴之【宮】</note><app n="0782040"><lem wit="【大】">服</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">服之</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">嚴之</rdg></app>者，<note type="orig" n="0782041" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔中有…者〕九字－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note type="mod" n="0782041" resp="CBETA">〔中有…者〕九字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0782041" cb:word-count="9"><lem wit="【大】">中
<pb xml:id="T14.0512.0782c" n="0782c" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0782c01"/>有取灰土而自坌者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782042" type="orig">〔中〕－【宮】</note><app n="0782042"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>有自<note type="orig" n="0782043" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">總＝㨑【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782043" resp="CBETA">總＝㨑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782043"><lem wit="【大】">總</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">㨑</rdg></app>拔其髮者，
<lb n="0782c02" ed="T"/><note n="0782044" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔中有…有〕十五字－【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782044">中有說王順政治國不枉人民者中有復＝復【聖】</note><app n="0782044"><lem wit="【大】">中有說王順<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0782045" place="foot text">政＝正【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782045">政＝正【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782045"><lem wit="【大】">政</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">正</rdg></app>治國不枉人民者，中<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782046">有復＝復有【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782046">有復＝復有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782046"><lem wit="【大】">有復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">復有</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">復</rdg></app>
<lb n="0782c03" ed="T"/>言：「諸小國等失其覆護！王中尊王今已崩
<lb n="0782c04" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782047" resp="Taisho">背＝皆【聖】</note><app n="0782047"><lem wit="【大】">背</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">皆</rdg></app>，國失威神。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0782c0406">時，諸釋子以眾香汁洗浴王
<lb n="0782c05" ed="T"/>身，纏以劫<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782048" type="orig">波＝婆【聖】</note><app n="0782048"><lem wit="【大】">波</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">婆</rdg></app>育<note resp="Taisho" n="0782049" type="orig" place="foot text">㲲＝疊【聖】</note><app n="0782049"><lem wit="【大】">㲲</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">疊</rdg></app>及諸繒<note resp="Taisho" n="0782050" type="orig" place="foot text">帛＝綵【聖】</note><app n="0782050"><lem wit="【大】">帛</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">綵</rdg></app>，而以棺斂；
<lb n="0782c06" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782051" type="orig">作＝於【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782051" resp="CBETA">作＝於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782051"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">於</rdg></app>師子座七寶莊<note type="orig" n="0782052" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">挍＝嚴【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782052" type="mod" resp="CBETA">挍＝嚴【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782052"><lem wit="【大】">挍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">嚴</rdg></app>，真珠羅網垂繞其
<lb n="0782c07" ed="T"/>傍，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782053" type="orig">〔便〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782053">〔便〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0782053"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>舉棺<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782054" type="orig">置＝著【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782054" type="mod" resp="CBETA">置＝著【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782054"><lem wit="【大】">置</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg></app>於師子座上，散華燒香。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0782c0715">佛共
<lb n="0782c08" ed="T"/>難陀在喪頭前肅恭而立，阿難、羅云住在
<lb ed="T" n="0782c09"/>喪足。難陀長跪，白佛言：「父王養我，願聽難
<lb ed="T" n="0782c10"/>陀擔父王棺。」阿難合掌，前白佛言：「唯願聽
<lb ed="T" n="0782c11"/>我擔伯父棺。」羅<app type="star" corresp="#0781017"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">雲</rdg></app>復前，而白佛言：「<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782055" type="orig">〔唯〕－【宮】</note><app n="0782055"><lem wit="【大】">唯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>願聽
<lb ed="T" n="0782c12"/>我擔<note resp="Taisho" n="0782056" type="orig" place="foot text">祖王＝父王【聖】</note><app n="0782056"><lem wit="【大】">祖王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">父王</rdg></app>棺。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0782c13"/><p xml:id="pT14p0782c1301">爾時，世尊念當來世，人民兇暴，不報父母
<lb n="0782c14" ed="T"/>育養之恩。為<note n="0782057" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔是〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782057">〔是〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782057"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>不孝之者，為是當來眾生
<lb ed="T" n="0782c15"/>之等，設禮法故，如來躬身自欲擔於父王
<lb n="0782c16" ed="T"/>之棺，即時三千大千世界六種震動，一切
<lb ed="T" n="0782c17"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782058" type="orig">眾山駊騀＝諸山岠峨【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0782058">眾山駊騀＝諸山岠峨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782058"><lem wit="【大】">眾山駊騀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諸山岠峨</rdg></app>涌沒，如水上船。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0782c1711" rend="inline">爾時欲界一切
<lb n="0782c18" ed="T"/>諸天與無央數百千眷屬，俱來赴喪：北方
<lb n="0782c19" ed="T"/>天<note n="0782059" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">王毘沙門＝毘沙門王【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0782059" resp="CBETA">王毘沙門＝毘沙門王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782059"><lem wit="【大】">王毘沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">毘沙門王</rdg></app>，將諸夜叉、鬼神之等億百千
<lb ed="T" n="0782c20"/>眾，俱來赴喪；東方天王提頭賴吒，從諸伎
<lb n="0782c21" ed="T"/>樂鬼神之等億百千眾，俱來赴喪；南方天
<lb ed="T" n="0782c22"/>王毘<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0782060" type="orig">樓＝留【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0782060" type="mod">樓＝留【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782060"><lem wit="【大】">樓</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">留</rdg></app>勒叉，<note place="foot text" n="0782061" type="orig" resp="Taisho">從＝將【宮】</note><app n="0782061"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">將</rdg></app><note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0782062" resp="Taisho">鳩＝究【聖】</note><app n="0782062"><lem wit="【大】">鳩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">究</rdg></app>槃荼鬼神之等億百千
<pb ed="T" n="0783a" xml:id="T14.0512.0783a"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0783a01"/>眾，俱來赴喪；西方天王毘留<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0783001" place="foot text">婆＝博【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783001" type="mod" resp="CBETA">婆＝博【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783001"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">博</rdg></app>叉，<note n="0783002" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">從＝將【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0783002">從＝將【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783002"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">將</rdg></app>諸龍
<lb ed="T" n="0783a02"/>神億百千眾，俱來赴喪，皆共發哀，舉聲啼
<lb ed="T" n="0783a03"/>哭。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0783a0302">時，四天王竊共<note n="0783003" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">思＝私【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0783003" resp="CBETA">思＝私【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783003"><lem wit="【大】">思</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">私</rdg></app>議：「瞻望世尊，為當來
<lb ed="T" n="0783a04"/>世諸不孝順父母者故，以大慈悲，現自躬身
<lb ed="T" n="0783a05"/>擔父王棺。」時，四天王<note resp="Taisho" n="0783004" type="orig" place="foot text">俱共＝同時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783004" type="mod" resp="CBETA">俱共＝同時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783004"><lem wit="【大】">俱共</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">同時</rdg></app>長跪，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0783005">〔同時發聲〕－【宮】</note><app n="0783005"><lem wit="【大】">同時發
<lb n="0783a06" ed="T"/>聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>俱白佛言：「唯然，世尊！願聽我等擔父王
<lb n="0783a07" ed="T"/>棺。所以然者？我等亦是佛之弟子，<note place="foot text" n="0783006" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔亦復〕－【聖】</note><app n="0783006"><lem wit="【大】">亦復</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>從
<lb n="0783a08" ed="T"/>佛聞法意解，得法眼淨，成須陀洹。以是之
<lb ed="T" n="0783a09"/>故，我曹<note type="orig" n="0783007" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">宜＝儀【聖】</note><app n="0783007"><lem wit="【大】">宜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">儀</rdg></app>擔父王之棺。」</p>
<lb n="0783a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0783a1001">爾時世尊，聽四天王擔父王棺。時，四天王各
<lb n="0783a11" ed="T"/>自變身，如人形像，以手擎棺，擔在肩上，舉
<lb ed="T" n="0783a12"/>國人民，一切大眾，莫不啼哭。</p>
<lb n="0783a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0783a1301">爾時，世尊威光益顯，如萬日並。如來躬身
<lb n="0783a14" ed="T"/>手執香爐，在喪前行，出詣葬所靈鷲山上。
<lb n="0783a15" ed="T"/>有千阿羅漢，以神足力乘虛來<note n="0783008" type="orig" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">至＝詣【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0783008" type="mod">至＝詣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783008"><lem wit="【大】">至</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">詣</rdg></app>，稽首佛
<lb n="0783a16" ed="T"/>足，復白佛言：「唯願世尊勅使何事！」時，佛便
<lb n="0783a17" ed="T"/>告<note type="orig" n="0783009" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0783009" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783009"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>阿羅漢：「汝等<note type="orig" n="0783010" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">疾＝速【聖】</note><app n="0783010"><lem wit="【大】">疾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">速</rdg></app>往大海渚上，取牛頭
<lb n="0783a18" ed="T"/>栴檀種種香木。」即<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig" n="0783011">受教勅＝便受教【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0783011" resp="CBETA">受教勅＝便受教【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783011"><lem wit="【大】">受教勅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">便受教</rdg></app>，如彈指頃，各到
<lb ed="T" n="0783a19"/>大海，共取香薪，屈伸臂頃，便<app corresp="#0782025" type="star"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">以</rdg></app>來到。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0783a1915">佛與
<lb n="0783a20" ed="T"/>大眾共積香薪，舉棺置上，放火焚之。一切
<lb n="0783a21" ed="T"/>大眾見火<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0783012" resp="Taisho">盛＝熾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783012" type="mod" resp="CBETA">盛＝熾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783012"><lem wit="【大】">盛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">熾</rdg></app>然，<note type="orig" n="0783013" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">皆＋（同）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0783013">皆＋（同）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783013"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">皆同</rdg></app>向佛前宛轉自撲，益
<lb n="0783a22" ed="T"/>更悲哭。有得道者，皆<note resp="Taisho" n="0783014" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝悉【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0783014">自＝悉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783014"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悉</rdg></app>慶幸；未獲道者，心
<lb ed="T" n="0783a23"/><note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0783015" place="foot text">戰＝顫【元】【明】</note><app n="0783015"><lem wit="【大】">戰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">顫</rdg></app>惶怖，衣毛為竪。</p>
<lb n="0783a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0783a2401"><note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0783016" resp="Taisho">爾時＝於是【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0783016">爾時＝於是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783016"><lem wit="【大】">爾時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">於是</rdg></app>世尊，告<note resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0783017" place="foot text">眾會＝大眾【三】【宮】，四眾會【聖】</note><note n="0783017" type="mod" resp="CBETA">眾會＝大眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝四眾會【聖】</note><app n="0783017"><lem wit="【大】">眾會</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">大眾</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">四眾會</rdg></app>曰：「世皆無常，苦空非身，
<lb ed="T" n="0783a25"/>無有堅固，如幻如化，如熱時炎，如水中月，
<lb ed="T" n="0783a26"/>命不久居。汝等諸人！勿見此火便以為熱，
<lb n="0783a27" ed="T"/>諸欲之火極復過此。是故，<note type="orig" n="0783018" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">汝等當＝當勤而【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0783018" resp="CBETA">汝等當＝當勤而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783018"><lem wit="【大】">汝等當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">當勤而</rdg></app>自勸勉，
<lb ed="T" n="0783a28"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0783019" type="orig">永離＝求離【聖】</note><app n="0783019"><lem wit="【大】">永離</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">求離</rdg></app>生死，乃得大安。」<note resp="Taisho" n="0783020" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝是【宮】</note><app n="0783020"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>火焚燒大王身已。</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0783a29"/><p xml:id="pT14p0783a2901">爾時，諸王各各皆持五百瓶乳，以用滅火。火
<pb xml:id="T14.0512.0783b" n="0783b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0783b01" ed="T"/>滅之後，競共收骨，盛置金凾，即於其上便
<lb n="0783b02" ed="T"/>共起塔，懸繒幡蓋及種種鈴，供養塔廟。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0783b0216">時諸
<lb ed="T" n="0783b03"/>大眾同時發聲，俱白佛言：「大淨飯王今已
<lb n="0783b04" ed="T"/>命終，神生何所？唯願世尊分別解說！」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0783b0415" rend="inline">於<note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0783021" resp="Taisho">時火焚燒＝焚【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0783021"><!--CBETA todo type: None-->時火焚燒＝焚【宮】</note>時，
<lb ed="T" n="0783b05"/>世尊告眾會曰：「父王淨飯是清淨人，生淨
<lb n="0783b06" ed="T"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0783022" type="orig">居天眾會＝居天【宋】【明】【宮】，世界【元】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0783022" type="mod">居天眾會＝居天【宋】【明】【宮】，＝世界【元】</note><app n="0783022"><lem wit="【大】">居天。」<note place="foot text" n="0783023" type="orig" resp="Taisho">〔眾會〕－【聖】</note><app n="0783023"><lem wit="【大】">眾會</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【宮】">居天</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">世界</rdg></app>聞是語已，便捨愁毒。</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT14p0783b0613">佛說經
<lb ed="T" n="0783b07"/>竟，諸天、龍、神及四天王、所將眷屬，世間人
<lb ed="T" n="0783b08"/>民一切大眾為佛作禮，各自<note resp="Taisho" n="0783024" type="orig" place="foot text">還＝而【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0783024" type="mod">還＝而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0783024"><lem wit="【大】">還</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】">而</rdg></app>去。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="T" n="0783b09"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="001"><cb:jhead><note place="foot text" type="orig" n="0783025" resp="Taisho">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0783025"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】【聖】"><space quantity="0"></space></rdg></app>淨飯王般涅槃經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>